03:34.714 --> 03:40.220 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: In a later
speech, Mr. Obama
argued greater freedom would
benefit the communist

03:40.253 --> 03:45.125 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
