36:00.025 --> 36:06.865 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHAD KARGES: Malheur Refuge is
about migratory
birds, and so this basin is one
of the most

36:06.898 --> 36:12.270 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
