one in Harney

36:43.401 --> 36:48.139 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
County. There's a long, proud
tradition of
ranching here, and cattle and
haying are the

36:48.173 --> 36:51.443 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
