44:41.913 --> 44:43.648 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: What did you see?

44:43.681 --> 44:47.652 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HOPE JAHREN: My very earliest
