45:57.755 --> 45:59.490 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
HOPE JAHREN: Yes, yes, yes.

45:59.523 --> 46:03.127 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Seeing colors
around us. And
yet, most of us -- maybe I
should speak for

46:03.160 --> 46:04.895 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
myself -- we don't see it every
day.

46:04.929 --> 46:06.030 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HOPE JAHREN: Yes. Yes.

46:06.063 --> 46:07.231 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: It's right there,
but we don't
see it.

46:07.265 --> 46:09.367 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HOPE JAHREN: But you used to.
You got away
from that.

46:09.400 --> 46:13.504 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
