common I meet
somebody who remembers looking
carefully at

46:18.776 --> 46:22.313 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a tree, and being near it, and
what it meant
to them, et cetera.

46:22.346 --> 46:26.684 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think one of the only
interesting things
about me is that I never lost
that. I never

46:26.717 --> 46:28.519 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
moved away from it.

46:28.552 --> 46:30.588 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: One of the
interesting things
about the way you write the
book, going back

46:30.621 --> 46:35.926 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
