differences
between us, right?

46:38.462 --> 46:39.697 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HOPE JAHREN: Yes, yes. It's
juxtaposed.

46:39.730 --> 46:41.499 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes.

46:41.532 --> 46:44.969 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HOPE JAHREN: I talk a little bit
about how
a plant establishes itself, and
the struggles

46:45.002 --> 46:46.904 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
it undergoes.

46:46.937 --> 46:51.509 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
