wonderful.

47:04.488 --> 47:09.360 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Some of the tough
parts, personal
parts about your struggles with
depression,

47:09.393 --> 47:10.094 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
