47:10.127 --> 47:11.629 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HOPE JAHREN: Yes. Yes.

47:11.662 --> 47:13.164 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: You had to work
hard to keep
this under management, right?

47:13.197 --> 47:14.298 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HOPE JAHREN: Yes.

47:14.331 --> 47:16.434 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: But it affected
