47:45.730 --> 47:51.001 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And then, of
course, for all
the wonder of scientific
discovery and research,

47:51.035 --> 47:54.238 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
