booing a worker, right?

47:54.271 --> 47:56.040 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HOPE JAHREN: Absolutely.

47:56.073 --> 47:59.310 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Of having to get
