the samples
accumulate right next to you.

48:18.362 --> 48:19.630 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: It's called "Lab
Girl."

48:19.663 --> 48:21.465 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HOPE JAHREN: Yes.

48:21.499 --> 48:24.568 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: You are a woman
