achieving the
same level of power and access
and privilege

48:50.327 --> 48:52.163 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in society.

48:52.196 --> 48:58.969 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so I think these things
apply to science,
in the same way that they apply
in who's in

48:59.003 --> 49:02.339 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
