place I was
comfortable, and this is the
place where I

49:39.810 --> 49:41.111 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
could do things.

49:41.145 --> 49:44.081 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: All right, the
book is "Lab
Girl."

49:44.114 --> 49:49.553 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Hope Jahren, thank you so much.

49:49.587 --> 49:53.190 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
